The paper is about object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves deep learning and iterative refinement, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on image datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
